---
import ImmersiveLayout from '../layouts/ImmersiveLayout.astro';
---

<ImmersiveLayout title="Agradecimientos">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-screen py-12">
        
        <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-fade-in-down">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-pink-600 mb-4">
                Agradecimientos
            </h1>
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Este proyecto fue posible gracias a la visión, guía y apoyo invaluable de nuestros asesores y colaboradores.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-7xl w-full px-4 mb-16">
            
            <div class="group relative bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-md border border-slate-700 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-all hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-purple-500/20">
                <div class="w-32 h-32 mb-6 rounded-full border-4 border-purple-500/30 overflow-hidden shadow-lg group-hover:border-purple-500 transition-colors bg-slate-700">
                    <img src="/images/team/rogelio.jpg" alt="Ing. Rogelio" class="w-full h-full object-cover" onError="this.style.display='none'" />
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Ing. Rogelio</h3>
                <p class="text-purple-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Asesor de Proyecto</p>
                <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    El ingeniero fue el que dio la idea de este proyecto.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="group relative bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-md border border-slate-700 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-all hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-pink-500/20">
                <div class="w-32 h-32 mb-6 rounded-full border-4 border-pink-500/30 overflow-hidden shadow-lg group-hover:border-pink-500 transition-colors bg-slate-700">
                    <img src="/images/team/liza.jpg" alt="Ing. Liza" class="w-full h-full object-cover" onError="this.style.display='none'" />
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Ing. Liza</h3>
                <p class="text-pink-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Presidenta de Academia de ing. Civil</p>
                <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    La ingeniera Liza fue asesora de redacción.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="group relative bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-md border border-slate-700 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-all hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-blue-500/20">
                <div class="w-32 h-32 mb-6 rounded-full border-4 border-blue-500/30 overflow-hidden shadow-lg group-hover:border-blue-500 transition-colors bg-slate-700">
                    <img src="/images/team/jose.jpg" alt="Ing. Jose Alejandro" class="w-full h-full object-cover" onError="this.style.display='none'" />
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Ing. Jose Alejandro Alvarez</h3>
                <p class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Colaborador Especial</p>
                <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    El ingeniero Jose fue el donante del <strong>Kit Mola</strong>.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="w-full group relative bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-md border border-slate-700 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-all hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-emerald-500/20">
                <div class="w-32 h-32 mb-6 rounded-full border-4 border-emerald-500/30 overflow-hidden shadow-lg group-hover:border-emerald-500 transition-colors bg-slate-700">
                    <img src="/images/team/autora.jpg" alt="Autora de Tesis" class="w-full h-full object-cover" onError="this.style.display='none'" />
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Evelin Noemi Tolentino Ortiz</h3>
                <p class="text-emerald-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Investigación y Estructura</p>
                <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Desarrolladora de la estructura intelectual del proyecto. La totalidad del contenido técnico está fundamentado en su trabajo de tesis.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="w-full group relative bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-md border border-slate-700 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-all hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-orange-500/20">
                <div class="w-32 h-32 mb-6 rounded-full border-4 border-orange-500/30 overflow-hidden shadow-lg group-hover:border-orange-500 transition-colors bg-slate-700">
                    <img src="/images/team/ram.png" alt="Editor de Video" class="w-full h-full object-cover" onError="this.style.display='none'" />
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Ing. Christian Ramsés Reyero</h3>
                <p class="text-orange-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Producción Multimedia</p>
                <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Encargado de la edición y post-producción de los videos explicativos.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="w-full group relative bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-md border border-slate-700 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-all hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-cyan-500/20">
                <div class="w-32 h-32 mb-6 rounded-full border-4 border-cyan-500/30 overflow-hidden shadow-lg group-hover:border-cyan-500 transition-colors bg-slate-700">
                    <img src="/images/team/vertex.png" alt="Diseñador Web" class="w-full h-full object-cover" onError="this.style.display='none'" />
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Vertex</h3>
                <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Diseño y Desarrollo Web</p>
                <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Responsable de la arquitectura, diseño de interfaz (UI) y experiencia de usuario (UX). Participantes: David de Jesus Perez Compean y Jean Carlo Garibay González.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>

        <a href="/repaso/menu" class="group relative px-8 py-4 bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-600 rounded-full font-bold text-white transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg border border-slate-500 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span>Volver al Menú Principal</span>
        </a>

    </div>
</ImmersiveLayout>